2%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20family%20spent%20%245%2C000%20on%20a%205-night%20vacation%20in%20Hawaii%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20that's%20after%20we%20were%20able%20to%20save%20%247%2C600%20on%20accommodations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20Disney%20Aulani%20resort%20with%20palm%20trees%20and%20greenery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671faf329b3250dbbcea816b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisney%20Aulani%20was%20beautiful%2C%20and%20I'm%20glad%20we%20were%20able%20to%20save%20money%20on%20our%20stay.%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20family%20went%20to%20Hawaii%20and%20spent%20about%20%245%2C000%20on%20airfare%2C%20a%20rental%20car%2C%20food%2C%20and%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20used%20Disney%20Vacation%20Club%20points%20to%20get%20a%20villa%20for%20five%20nights%20that%20was%20valued%20at%20%247%2C630.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAside%20from%20taking%20more%20photos%20and%20cooking%20more%20food%2C%20there's%20not%20much%20I'd%20change%20about%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-aulani-resort-review-worth-it-for-adults-hawaii-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAulani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Disney's%20resort%20in%20Oahu's%20quiet%20Ko%20Olina%20area%2C%20has%20been%20on%20my%20family's%20bucket%20list%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20opened%20in%202011%20and%20cost%20an%20estimated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.nytimes.com%2Fmediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com%2F2011%2F08%2F16%2Fnew-disney-vacation-resort-in-hawaii-faces-possible-losses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24850%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build.%20Today%2C%20the%2021-acre%20property%20has%20more%20than%20800%20rooms%20(including%20suites%20and%20villas).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20of%20four%20finally%20visited%20the%20resort%20in%20June.%20Our%20trip%20was%20pricey%2C%20but%20it%20went%20smoothly%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20great%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20expenses%20are%20roughly%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAirfare%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%242%2C284%20for%20two%20round-trip%20flights%20from%20San%20Antonio%20to%20Honolulu%20after%20using%20points%20for%20our%20kids'%20tickets%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERental%20car%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%24464%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20and%20drinks%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%241%2C193%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActivities%20and%20excursions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%241%2C058%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHotel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%240%20for%20five%20nights%20at%20Aulani%20after%20using%20points%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20how%20we%20spent%20our%20money%20and%20what%20we'd%20do%20differently%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETransportation%20was%20the%20priciest%20part%20of%20our%20trip%20even%20though%20we%20only%20paid%20for%20two%20flights.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aulani%20lagoon%20at%20sunset%20with%20view%20of%20palm%20trees%20in%20background%20and%20people%20in%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671fae209b3250dbbcea80e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20hotel%20was%20right%20along%20the%20ocean.%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20family%20of%20four%20spent%20%242%2C285%20to%20fly%20from%20San%20Antonio%20to%20Honolulu%20because%20we%20only%20had%20to%20buy%20two%20tickets.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20paid%20%241%2C142%20each%2C%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupgraded-kid-to-business-class-future-flights-ruined-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20points%20for%20my%20kids'%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20transportation%2C%20we%20also%20chose%20to%20rent%20a%20car.%20We%20didn't%20necessarily%20need%20it%2C%20but%20it%20meant%20we%20didn't%20pay%20for%20rideshares%20during%20our%20vacation%20%E2%80%94%20including%20ones%20to%20get%20us%20to%20and%20from%20the%20airport%20about%2025%20minutes%20from%20our%20resort.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20used%20our%20rental%20car%20to%20go%20grocery%20shopping%2C%20visit%20Diamond%20Head%2C%20and%20get%20to%20a%20beach%20in%20the%20Honolulu%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20used%20Disney%20Vacation%20Club%20points%20to%20book%20our%20room%2C%20which%20saved%20us%20thousands.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20Aulani%20hotel%20exterior%20with%20small%20waterfall%20feature%20and%20wood%20accents%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671fadbd01ea6d83dee47b86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20stayed%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20villa%20at%20Aulani.%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-saving-hack-disney-hotels-disney-vacation-club-frequent-guest-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20Vacation%20Club%20(DVC)%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20timeshare%20program%20where%20members%20buy%20points%20to%20use%20on%20stays%20at%20Disney%20resorts%20%E2%80%94%20since%202018.%20We%20usually%20buy%20175%20points%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20trip%20during%20Hawaii's%20high%20season%2C%20a%20one-bedroom%20villa%20at%20Aulani%20cost%2050%20points%20per%20night%2C%20making%20our%20five-night%20stay%20250%20points.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20more%20than%20we%20earn%20in%20a%20year%20so%20we%20borrowed%20against%20a%20future%20year%20to%20have%20enough%20points%20for%20our%20stay.%20If%20we'd%20booked%20our%20room%20without%20DVC%20and%20paid%20cash%2C%20we%20would've%20spent%20%241%2C526%20per%20night%20for%20a%20total%20of%20%247%2C630.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20villa%20was%20quite%20nice.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Booth%20next%20to%20kitchen%20with%20oven%2C%20microwave%2C%20coffee%20maker%2C%20plus%20extra%20seating%20with%20light%20above%20it%20in%20Disney%20Aulani%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671fadf79b3250dbbcea80cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20plenty%20of%20space%20to%20cook%20and%20eat%20meals%20in%20our%20villa.%20%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-villa-is-it-worth-it-wilderness-lodge-photos-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-bedroom%20villa%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20separate%20bedroom%20with%20a%20king-sized%20bed%2C%20a%20living%20room%20with%20a%20sofa%20sleeper%2C%20and%20a%20twin-sized%20bed%20built%20into%20a%20credenza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20balcony%20overlooking%20the%20pool%20and%20lagoon%2C%20a%20full%20kitchen%2C%20and%20a%20washer-dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20also%20had%20a%20split%20bathroom%20with%20the%20shower%20and%20toilet%20separated%20from%20the%20tub.%20Each%20part%20of%20the%20split%20bathroom%20had%20a%20sink%20and%20vanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20purchased%20a%20few%20groceries%20for%20our%20room%2C%20but%20that%20didn't%20save%20us%20much%20money.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221435%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rainbow%20shave%20ice%20shaped%20like%20Mickey%20mouse's%20head%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671fae569b3250dbbcea8116%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221076%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20food%20wasn't%20very%20cheap.%20%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20to%20save%20by%20buying%20groceries%20instead%20of%20dining%20out%20every%20meal%2C%20but%20this%20didn't%20help%20much.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-grocery-store-food-prices-haawaii-eggs-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaii%20imports%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20groceries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20they%20can%20get%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20grocery%20bill%20was%20%24101%2C%20but%20we%20still%20spent%20over%20%241%2C000%20on%20food%20and%20beverages%20at%20Aulani's%20various%20restaurants%20and%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20mostly%20ate%20at%20the%20property's%20more%20affordable%20restaurants.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Off%20the%20hook%20menu%20with%20cocktails%2C%20sandwiches%20being%20held%20by%20woman's%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671faebea0a0cc14f224579b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELike%20many%20restaurants%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20Aulani's%20menu%20items%20were%20pretty%20pricey.%20%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAulani%20has%20four%20table-service%20restaurants%20and%20a%20luau%20that%20includes%20dinner%20and%20a%20show.%20Food%20is%20also%20served%20at%20quick-service%20spots%20and%20snack%20kiosks%20at%20the%20pools%20and%20near%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20skipped%20Aulani's%20pricier%20sit-down%20restaurants%20with%20tasting%20menus%20%3Cspan%3EAMA'AMA%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Makahiki.%20Instead%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20quick-service%20Ulu%20Cafe%20and%20casual%20outdoor%20eatery%20Off%20the%20Hook.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20food%20at%20Aulani%20was%20expensive.%20At%20Ulu%20Cafe%2C%20bagel%20sandwiches%20start%20at%20%2417%2C%20and%20most%20entr%C3%A9es%20at%20Off%20the%20Hook%20were%20over%20%2420.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20our%20order%20of%20two%20poke%20bowls%2C%20two%20small%20pizzas%2C%20and%20t