ation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20Tuesday%20in%20Delaware's%20Chancery%20Court%2C%20alleges%20that%20Orlando%20and%20ARC%20Global%20have%20failed%20to%20transfer%20what%20is%20owed%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%2075%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20the%20total%20approximate%208.1%20million%20shares%20of%20stock%20in%20Trump%20Media%20that%20ARC%20Global%20owns%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20Media%20is%20the%20operator%20of%20Trump's%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-truth-social-tmtg-stock-wealth-election-harris-x-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrlando%2C%20his%20attorneys%2C%20and%20attorneys%20for%20ARC%20Global%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accuses%20the%20defendants%20of%20%26quot%3Bcoordinated%20and%20intentional%20theft%20of%20stock%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Begregious%20breaches%20of%20fiduciary%20duties%26quot%3B%20by%20Orlando.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrlando%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20%26quot%3Borchestrated%20a%20scheme%20with%20the%20other%20Defendants%20to%20divert%20the%20majority%20of%20ARC%20ownership%20interest%20to%20himself%20and%20his%20family%20through%20a%20closely%20held%20alter-ego%20entity%20named%20Franlu%20LLC%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20Cayman%20Islands-based%20entity%20called%20Belsize%20Ventures%20Ltd.%20Franlu%20and%20Belsize%20are%20also%20named%20as%20defendants%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20doing%20so%2C%20Orlando%20intentionally%20breached%20his%20fiduciary%20duties%20owed%20to%20Plaintiffs%20by%20diluting%20the%20ownership%20interests%20of%20the%20Plaintiffs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20%26quot%3BSpecifically%2C%20as%20Managing%20Member%20of%20ARC%2C%20Orlando%20conveyed%20roughly%2046%25%20of%20ARC's%20membership%20interest%20to