ing%20comeback%20after%20a%204-year%20gap%20to%20get%20re-elected%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%20Mr%20Trump's%20win%20will%20almost%20certainly%20have%20an%20effect%20on%20the%20global%20order%20and%20significantly%20impact%20policy%20and%20trade%20for%20most%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20win%20will%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20globalisation.%20Sharing%20his%20views%20on%20this%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20there%20are%20four%20aspects%20on%20how%20India%20views%20this%3A%20Firstly%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20already%20a%20reordering%20of%20supply%20chains%20which%20was%20taking%20place%20(globally).%20It%20is%20very%20likely%20that%20this%20will%20get%20accelerated%20after%20the%20election%20result%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20very%20candid%20with%20you%2C%20that%20some%20of%20this%20will%20be%20somewhat%20disruptive%2C%20but%20we%20in%20India%20perceive%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20because%20having%20kind%20of%20missed%20the%20manufacturing%20bus%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20early%202000s%2C%20we%20do%20think%20that%20this%20reordering%20of%20supply%20chain%20gives%20us%20a%20sort%20of%20second%20bite%20of%20the%20apple.%20And%20maybe%20this%20time%20around%2C%20starting%20with%20Apple%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20better%20than%20we%20were%20doing%20earlier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly%2C%20there%20will%20be%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20more%20geopolitical%20hedging.%20that%2C%20what%20will%20inevitably%20happen%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20policies%20which%20we%20can%2C%20at%20least%20those%20parts%20of%20it%20we%20can%20safely%20predict%2C%20will%20be%20that%20many%20more%20of%20us%20would%20be%20seeking%20more%20relationships%20(globally)%20to%20keep%20life%20stable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20minister%20went%20on%20to%20highlight%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20digital%20age%20we%20all%20live%20in%2C%20explaining%20that%20digital%20payment%20platforms%20will%20ultimately%20become%20very%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20third%20aspect%20pertains%20to%20the%20digital%20digital%20side%2C%20and%20the%20digital%20side%20now%20pretty%20much%20covers%20everything.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20been%20happening%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20intensify%20is%20about%20trust%2C%20and%20what%20accompanies%20the%20digital%20aspect%20of%20a%20product%20or%20service%20or%20technology%20will%20come%20under%20greater%20scrutiny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3BDigital%20payment%20platforms%2C%20for%20example%2C%20would%20become%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20much%20more%20valuable.%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20platform%20to%20use%20and%20share%20with%20whom%2C%20becomes%20an%20important%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20aspect%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20mobility.%20Speaking%20about%20it%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20demographic%20unevenness%20of%20the%20world%20is%20beginning%20to%20bite%20us%20that%20there%20would%20be%2C%20economies%20where%20the%20demand%20would%20be%20high.%20In%20those%20countries%2C%20the%20talents%20may%20not%20be%20plentiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20different%20in%20other%20places%2C%20and%20what%20will%20happen%2C%20and%20is%20already%20happening%20is%20that%20we%20will%20be%20moving%2C%20perhaps%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20to%20a%20much%20more%20integrated%20global%20workplace%20that%20many%20countries%20--%20even%20a%20United%20States%20under%20Donald%20Trump%20--%20will%20make%20a%20distinction%20in%20immigration%20and%20mobility%20for%20them.%20An%20economically-justified%20mobility%20will%20have%20to%20be%20fostered%20by%20those%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20minister%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B