d%20actively%20campaigned%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%20elections.%20Trump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-adopt-musks-proposal-government-efficiency-commission-wsj-reports-2024-09-05%2F%5C%22%3Efloated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20idea%20of%20making%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20bureaucratic%20purge.%20He%20wants%20Musk%20to%20head%20an%20efficiency%20commission%2C%20whose%20main%20job%20will%20be%20to%20shrink%20government%20expenditure%2C%20including%20by%20potentially%20firing%20thousands%20of%20career%20bureaucrats.%20Trump%20wants%20to%20rid%20the%20US%20government%20of%20what%20he%20believes%20is%20a%20cabal%20of%20federal%20employees%2C%20a%20deep%20state%20that%20pursues%20its%20own%20agenda.%20One%20of%20his%20allies%2C%20Kash%20Patel%2C%20who%20is%20helping%20in%20the%20regime%20transition%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F06%2Fpolitics%2Ftransition-donald-trump-jockeying%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Escreening%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20for%20potential%20positions%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20Patel%2C%20who%20has%20written%20a%20book%20%3Cem%3EGovernment%20Gangsters%3A%20The%20Deep%20State%2C%20the%20Truth%2C%20and%20the%20Battle%20for%20Our%20Democracy%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0himself%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20angling%20to%20be%20Trump's%20chief%20spook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20responded%20to%20Trump's%20victory%20in%20typical%20style%3B%20a%20picture%20of%20himself%20carrying%20a%20kitchen%20sink%20with%20the%20Oval%20Office%20in%20the%20background%20and%20the%20line%3A%20%E2%80%98Let%20that%20sink%20in!'%20That%20was%20a%20throwback%20to%20when%20he%20bought%20Twitter%20and%20walked%20into%20its%20headquarters%20with%20a%20sink.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden's%20Battle%20With%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20victory%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20remarkable%20comeback%20in%20US%20political%20history.%20The%20epochal%20story's%20side%20track%20is%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20not-so-quiet%20battle%20that%20Big%20Tech%20has%20been%20waging%20with%20Washington%20during%20the%20entire%20term%20of%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20President's%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20Lina%20Khan%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20(FTC)%2C%20relentlessly%20pursued%20companies%20such%20as%20Facebook%2C%20Google%20and%20Apple%2C%20wielding%20the%20antitrust%20law%20like%20an%20electric%20whip.%20Billionaire%20CEOs%20sat%20shuddering%20before%20Congressional%20committees%20as%20combative%20members%20dragged%20them%20over%20coals.%20A%20Republican-led%20House%20Judiciary%20Committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F05%2Ftechnology%2Felection-2024-ftc-lina-khan.html%5C%22%3Eaccused%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20weaponising%20the%20agency%20and%20pushing%20a%20far-left%20agenda.%20Khan%20and%20FTC%20occupied%20significant%20mind-space%20in%20the%20closing%20stages%20of%20the%20presidential%20campaign.%20She%20will%20be%20fired%20soon%2C%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X%20a%20day%20before%20the%20vote.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entry%20of%20Musk%2C%20along%20with%20Vice-President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20signals%20the%20deepest%20incursion%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20into%20US%20national%20politics.%20Vance%2C%20who%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fpolitics%2Fworld%2Fnews%2Fi-reread-jd-vances-hillbilly-elegy-he-hasnt-transformed-as-much-as-you-think-%2Farticleshow%2F111845075.cms%5C%22%3Ederisively%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%20heroin%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F04%2Finside-the-new-right-where-peter-thiel-is-placing-his-biggest-bets%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Ddhtwitter%26utm_content%3Dapp.dashhudson.com%2Fvanityfair%2Flibrary%2Fmedia%2F470296154%5C%22%3Ehandpicked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20groomed%20and%20funded%20to%20first%20become%20Ohio%20governor%20and%20then%20Trump's%20running%20mate%20by%20libertarian%20founder%20of%20payment%20firm%20PayPal%20and%20data%20analytics%20company%20Palantir%20Technologies%2C%20Peter%20Thiel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReign%20Of%20The%20Unpredictables%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Trump%20has%20no%20love%20lost%20for%20entrepreneurs%20such%20as%20Mark%20Zuckerburg.%20His%20pals%2C%20Musk%20and%20Thiel%2C%20checked%20out%20of%20%E2%80%9CWoke%E2%80%9D%20California%20long%20ago.%20Trump%20has%20reversed%20his%20intention%20to%20ban%20Chinese%20social%20media%20app%20TikTok%2C%20a%20Meta%20rival%2C%20ostensibly%20after%20being%20persuaded%20by%20investor%20Jeffrey%20Yass%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20juicy%20slice%20of%20its%20parent%20Bytedance.%20The%20libertarian%20billionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frepublican-hedge-fund-owner-tiktok-investor-yass-emerges-top-donor-us-election-2024-03-21%2F%5C%22%3Edonated%20over%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2446%20billion%20to%20Republican%20causes.%20With%20the%20Senate%20and%20House%20also%20firmly%20packed%20with%20tens%20of%20elected%20legislators%20backed%20by%20billionaire%20tech%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors%2C%20the%20power%20shift%20is%20all%20too%20evident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Trump%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20uncontrollable%20wrecking%20ball%2C%20Musk%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20even%20more%20unpredictable.%20While%20countries%20the%20world%20over%20are%20bracing%20for%20the%20Trump%20impact%2C%20whether%20on%20tariffs%2C%20movement%20of%20professionals%2C%20technology%20transfer%2C%20or%20military%20deployment%2C%20Musk's%20influence%20if%20he%20joins%20the%20administration%20is%20an%20even%20bigger%20unknown.%20As%20the%20richest%20man%20on%20earth%20with%20a%20%24286%20billion%20fortune%20as%20of%20election%20day%20and%20business%20interests%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20Musk%20has%20close%20ties%20with%20many%20leaders%2C%20including%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20abruptly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-shocked-musks-surprise-china-visit-leaves-them-spurned-2024-04-30%2F%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20a%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20India%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20only%20to%20head%20to%20Beijing%20for%20confabulations%20with%20the%20Chinese%20leadership.%20That%20sojourn%20cleared%20Tesla's%20path%20in%20that%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20refused%20Tesla%20and%20Starlink%20lower%20entry%20barriers%20and%20requests%20for%20special%20treatment.%20Trump%20is%20known%20to%20intervene%20with%20other%20countries%20on%20behalf%20of%20American%20businesses.%20In%20his%20previous%20term%2C%20he%20had%20pushed%20India%20for%20concessions%20to%20Harley%20Davidson%20motorcycles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBFFs%2C%20But%20Probably%20Not%20For%20Long%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20however%2C%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20to%20Trump%20as%20his%20business%20interests%20may%20clash%20with%20US%20foreign%20policy.%20For%20instance%2C%20Tesla's%20largest%20factory%20is%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20and%20another%20one%20is%20in%20Berlin.%20Both%20countries%20are%20bracing%20for%20higher%20tariff%20barriers%20under%20Trump.%20Musk%20also%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Frussia%2Fmusk-putin-secret-conversations-37e1c187%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20had%20secret%20dealings%20with%20Putin%2C%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20lobbied%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20friend%20Xi%20to%20switch%20off%20Taiwan's%20access%20to%20Starlink.%20Musk%20has%20also%20made%20statements%20that%20are%20contradictory%20to%20US%20interests%20and%20publicly%20stated%20positions%20on%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20antipathy%20towards%20green%20initiatives%20and%20abiding%20faith%20in%20petroleum%20may%20not%20augur%20well%20for%20Tesla's%20electric%2