%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20shared%20the%20ministry's%20answer%20to%20an%20unstarred%20question%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20March%202020%2C%20which%20quoted%20then%20junior%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20as%20saying%20the%20phrase%20is%20not%20used%20by%20the%20Ministry.%20%26quot%3BMr%20Fadnavis%20should%20think%20first%20and%20then%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20had%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20allegations%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi...%20proved%20to%20be%20true%20about%20his%20inclination%20towards%20urban%20naxals.%20He%20showed%20the%20'red%20book'%20and%20tried%20to%20seek%20help%20(politically)%20from%20urban%20naxals...%20What%20message%20could%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20wanted%20to%20give...%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20wasn't%20just%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20hitting%20out%3B%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Maharashtra%20spokesperson%2C%20Keshava%20Upadhye%20spewed%20fire%20at%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20vs%20Congress%20Over%20'Blank'%20Red%20Notebooks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20slammed%20his%20rivals%20for%20%26quot%3Bfake%20drama%26quot%3B%2C%20claiming%20the%20book%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20waved%20at%20the%20Samvidhan%20Samman%20Sammelan%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20and%20later%20distributed%20to%20people%2C%20was%20actually%20a%20blank%20notebook%20with%20a%20binding%20designed%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fa841ucko_devendra-fadnavis_625x300_16_March_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadavis%20(File).%3C%2F