.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-red-book-urban-naxals-maharashtra-assembly-election-devendra-fadnavis-bjps-urban-naxals-attack-after-row-over-red-book-at-rahul-gandhi-ev-6965311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'red%20book'%20threw%20up%20'red%20flags'%20Thursday%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20-%20and%20their%20allies%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20factions%20-%20squabble%20in%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%20November%2020%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-red-book-urban-naxals-maharashtra-assembly-election-devendra-fadnavis-bjps-urban-naxals-attack-after-row-over-red-book-at-rahul-gandhi-ev-6965311%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Calls%20Out%20Canada's%20Move%20Against%20Outlet%20That%20Interviewed%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResponding%20strongly%20to%20reports%20of%20social%20media%20handles%20and%20pages%20of%20an%20Australian%20news%20outlet%20being%20blocked%20in%20Canada%20hours%20after%20it%20carried%20a%20press%20conference%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20Australian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Penny%20Wong%20as%20well%20as%20an%20interview%20of%20the%20Indian%20minister%2C%20India%20has%20said%20such%20actions%20highlight%20Canada's%20hypocrisy%20towards%20freedom%20of%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20Australia%20visit%2C%20which%20ends%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20met%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20and%20also%20co-chaired%20the%2015th%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20Framework%20Dialogue%20with%20Ms%20Wong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20Australia%20Today%20being%20blocked%20in%20Canada%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20that%20social%20media%20handles%20and%20pages%20of%20this%20outlet%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20diaspora%20outlet%2C%20have%20been%20blocked%20and%20are%20not%20available%20for%20viewers%20in%20Canada.%20This%20happened%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20this%20particular%20handle%20carried%20the%20press%20conference%20of%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20with%20Penny%20Wong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20outlet%20had%20carried%20an%20interview%20with%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20as%20well%20as%20several%20articles%20on%20his%20visit%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20surprised.%20It%20looks%20strange%20to%20us.%20But%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20these%20are%20actions%20that%20yet%20again%20highlight%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20Canada%20towards%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20In%20his%20media%20interactions%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20spoke%20about%20three%20things%3A%20a%20pattern%20of%20Canada%20making%20allegations%20without%20evidence%2C%20the%20surveillance%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20-%20which%20he%20termed%20unacceptable%20-%20and%20the%20political%20space%20being%20given%20in%20Canada%20to%20anti-India%20elements.%20So%20you%20can%20draw%20your%20conclusions%20from%20that%20on%20why%20the%20Australia%20Today%20channel%20was%20blocked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20India%20had%20said%20some%20of%20its%20consular%20officials%20were%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20under%20audio%20and%20video%20surveillance.%20Terming%20the%20action%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20diplomatic%20conventions%2C%20India%20had%20said%20Canada%20could%20not%20hide%20behind%20technicalities%20to%20justify%20its%20harassment%20and%20intimidation%20and%20that%20a%20protest%20had%20been%20lodged%20with%20the%20Canadian%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%20also%20confirmed%20that%20some%20consular%20camps%20have%20been%20cancelled%20in%20Toronto%20because%20they%20did%20not%20get%20security%20assurance%20from%20Canada.%20The%20announcement%20came%20days%20after%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Brampton%2C%20where%20a%20consular%20camp%20was%20being%20held%2C%20on%20November%203.%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20also%20condemned%20the%20attack%20and%20criticised%20%26quot%3Bcowardly%20attempts%26quot%3B%20to%20intimidate%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Canada.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnTies%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20been%20strained%20since%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20claimed%20-%20without%20offering%20any%20evidence%20-%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3BIndian%20agents%26quot%3B%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20The%20allegation%20has%20been%20rubbished%20by%20New%20Delhi%20several%20times%20and%20it%20has%20asked%20Canada%20to%20produce%20evidence%20to%20back%20up%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20hit%20a%20new%20low%20last%20month%20when%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20was%20termed%20a%20%26quot%3Bperson%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20killing.%20India%20dismissed%20the%20fresh%20charge%20as%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%26quot%3B%20and%20withdrew%20the%20High%20Commissioner%20and%20some%20diplomats%20while%20expelling%20six%20Canadian%20officials%2C%20including%20Canada's%20acting%20High%20Commissioner%20Stewart%20Ross%20Wheeler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730981040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fd83eucg_s-jaishankar_625x300_02_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-australia-today-india-calls-out-canadas-move-against-australian-outlet-that-interviewed-s-jaishankar-6965431%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Responding%20strongly%20to%20reports%20of%20social%20media%20handles%20and%20pages%20of%20an%20Australian%20news%20outlet%20being%20blocked%20in%20Canada%2C%20India%20has%20said%20such%20a