s%20life-saving%20procedure%20involves%20removing%20blood%20from%20the%20body%20through%20a%20needle%2C%20passing%20it%20through%20a%20machine%20to%20filter%20out%20harmful%20substances%2C%20and%20then%20returning%20the%20clean%20blood%20to%20the%20body.%20Typically%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20necessary%20when%20kidney%20function%20declines%20significantly%2C%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20natural%20filtration%20is%20insufficient%20to%20support%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20problem%20of%20accessibility%20remains%2C%20the%20other%20concern%20is%20affordability.%20To%20provide%20dialysis%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Programme%20(PMNDP)%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%20April%202016.%20The%20programme%20has%20two%20components%3A%20Hemodialysis%20(HD)%20services%20and%20Peritoneal%20dialysis%20(PD)%20services.%20Under%20the%20PMNDP%2C%20the%20government%20has%20set%20up%201%2C530%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20still%20leaving%20a%20significant%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKey%20issues%20include%20high%20treatment%20costs%2C%20limited%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344858%2Fthe-hans-foundation-dialysis-chronic-kidney-disease-renal-care-centre-treat-underprivileged-rural-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accessibility%20barriers%20for%20patients%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20healthcare%20professionals.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20kidney%20disease%20and%20dialysis%20options%20further%20complicates%20timely%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20Dialysis%20Convenient%3A%20How%20VitusCare%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVitusCare%20provides%20three%20forms%20of%20patient%20care%3A%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20where%20they%20set%20up%20centres%20inside%20existing%20hospitals%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20(95%20percent%20of%20their%20centres)%2C%20standalone%20centres%20where%20they%20open%20facilities%20in%20areas%20without%20hospitals%2C%20and%20at-home%20dialysis%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20their%20most%20popular%20form%20of%20care%2C%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20Prabhat%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20a%20space%2C%20develop%20and%20prepare%20it.%20We%20employ%20support%20staff%20in%20the%20centres.%20Using%20a%20hub-and-spoke%20model%2C%20we%20monitor%20all%20centres%20through%20our%20central%20team%20in%20Gurgaon.%20We%20have%20an%20operations%20team%20that%20monitors%20each%20centre%2C%20ensuring%20quality%20through%20strict%20SOPs.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Ffit%3D1600%252C739%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22VitusCare%20works%20on%20a%20box-in-box%20model.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fw%3D1600%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp