Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMDA%20was%20founded%20in%201992%20when%20a%20group%20of%20parents%20of%20children%20with%20dyslexia%2C%20educationists%20empathetic%20to%20the%20cause%2C%20and%20philanthropists%20came%20together%20to%20actively%20help%20children%20address%20this%20condition%20and%20raise%20awareness%20about%20it%20to%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20was%20founded%20to%20take%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20help%20children%20with%20dyslexia.%20For%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20it%20has%20been%20providing%20remedial%20help%20and%20support%20to%20children%20with%20dyslexia%20and%20their%20parents%20through%20the%20Ananya%20Learning%20and%20Research%20Centre%20(ALRC).%20They%20have%20also%20been%20actively%20working%20towards%20spreading%20awareness%20to%20the%20community%20at%20large%2C%20helping%20schools%20set%20up%20resource%20rooms%20and%20conducting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309309%2Fcentral-square-foundation-teachers-guide-improves-learning-outcomes-nipun-bharat-mission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteacher%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20dyslexia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20MDA%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20dyslexia%20is%20a%20hidden%20%5Blearning%5D%20disability%20that%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20child%20to%20perform%20to%20his%2Fher%20actual%20potential%2C%20the%20underachievement%20of%20an%20otherwise%20intelligent%20child%20is%20puzzling%20to%20both%20teachers%20and%20parents%20alike.%20Timely%20identification%20and%20appropriate%20help%20will%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20continue%20