22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWastewater%20treatment%20is%20the%20key%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20conserve%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Phase%201%2C%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%20was%20installed%20to%20provide%20240%20kilo%20litres%20(2.4%20lakh%20litres)%20of%20water%20daily.%20In%20Phase%202%2C%20the%20project%20expanded%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20four%20more%20filter%20borewells%2C%20a%20reconstructed%2060%20kilolitres%20(KL)%20sump%2C%20and%20a%20new%20400%20KLD%20water%20treatment%20plant.%20The%20system%20now%20delivers%20640%20KL%20(6.4%20lakh)%20of%20water%20daily%2C%20benefiting%20the%20Devanahalli%20residents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20vision%20is%20to%20create%20a%20sustainable%20third%20source%20of%20water%20by%20utilising%20every%20drop%20of%20wastewater%20generated%20in%20our%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20break%20down%20the%20project%20into%20its%20finer%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20did%20we%20get%20here%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Biome%20has%20been%20doing%20is%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20old%20well%20near%20the%20Sihineeru%20Kere%20lake%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20over%20100%20years%20old.%20Due%20to%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20dryness%20and%20lack%20of%20water%20seepage%20into%20the%20well%2C%20people%20started%20using%20it%20to%20dispose%20of%20debris.%20Biome%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20local%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cleaned%20out%20this%20well%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20well%20was%20cleaned%20and%20treated%20wastewater%20was%20directed%20to%20the%20lake%2C%20the%20well%2C%20situated%20about%2025%20to%2030%20feet%20from%20the%20lake%2C%20began%20to%20fill%20as%20water%20seeped%20through%20the%20earth%20from%20the%20lake.%20This%20natural%20earth%20filtration%20helped%20fill%20the%20well.%20Biome%20then%20tested%20this%20well%20water%2C%20which%20met%20the%20IS%2010500%20standards.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20got%20involved%2C%20recognising%20the%20water%20quality%20and%20exploring%20how%20to%20make%20it%20usable%20for%20the%20public.%20Since%20the%20well%20water%20filtered%20through%20the%20earth%2C%20it%20was%20deemed%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20a%20two-phase%20project%20was%20initiated.%20The%20first%20phase%2C%20completed%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20was%20designed%20to%20recover%20200%20KL%20(2%20lakh%20litres)%20of%20water%20daily.%20Water%20from%20the%20well%20was%20processed%20through%20disk%20filtration%2C%20activated%20carbon%20filtration%20(with%20high%20iodine%20value)%2C%20UV%20(ultraviolet%20light%20disinfection)%20treatment%2C%20and%20basic%20chlorine%20disinfection%20before%20being%20sent%20to%20a%20sump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Ffit%3D1599%252C720%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20water%20shortage%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20with%20lake%20rejuvenation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fw%3D1599%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201599w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C135%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C225%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C346%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D1536%252C692%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C540%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0018-1730297279.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C68%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373571%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolutions%20to%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20shortage%3A%20Lake%20rejuvenation%20by%20employing%20treated%20wastewater%20is%20a%20core%20component%20of%20this%20model%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sump%20also%20received%20deep%20borewell%20water.%20In%20that%20area%2C%20deep%20borewells%2C%20which%20reach%20depths%20of%20around%201%2C000%20to%201%2C100%20feet%2C%20often%20contain%20fluoride%20and%20other%20contaminants%2C%20making%20the%20water%20usable%20only%20for%20bathing%20and%20similar%20purposes.%20Water%20from%20the%20sump%20was%20pumped%20to%20the%20entire%20Devanahalli%20town%2C%20which%20requires%20about%205.4%20to%206%20MLD%20of%20water%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBiome%20envisioned%20that%20by%20meeting%20just%2010%25%20of%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20water%20needs%2C%20they%20could%20demonstrate%20a%20viable%20model%20for%20small%20towns%20across%20India.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20where%20lakes%20and%20wastewater%20are%20available%2C%20communities%20could%20effectively%20use%20such%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhase%201%20was%20installed%20in%20July-August%202023%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20year%20of%20testing.%20Once%20it%20proved%20effective%2C%20Phase%202%20was%20launched%20in%20August%202024.%20Now%2C%20both%20phases%20are%20operational%2C%20supplying%20600%20KL%20or%206%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20next%20phase%2C%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20replicate%20this%20process%20at%20Doddakere%20Lake%2C%20a%20large%20lake%20with%20multiple%20unused%20wells%20currently%20filled%20with%20debris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20from%20lake%20to%20lake%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20is%20treated%20at%20the%20government-operated%20STP%20called%20Hebbal%20Nagawara%20Treatment%20Plant%20(HN%20Valley%20Treatment%20Plant).%20From%20this%20plant%2C%20it%20is%20pumped%20to%20Bagalur%20Lake%20through%20a%20pipeline%20and%20then%20from%20that%20lake%20it%20comes%20to%20Sihi%20Neerukere%20Lake.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20specific%20reason%20they%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lakes%20often%20dry%20up%2C%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20refill%20them%20is%20by%20pumping%20treated%20wastewater.%20Government-run%20STPs%20are%20required%20to%20meet%20certain%20qualities%20so%20that%20the%20wastewater%20they%20treat%20can%20be%20pumped%20into%20the%20lakes.%20Only%20if%20that%20quality%20is%20met%2C%20the%20treated%20wastewater%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20does%20treated%20wastewater%20require%20further%20dilution%20by%20rainwater%20in%20both%20Bagalur%20Lake%20and%20Sihi%20Neerukere%20Lake%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20the%20treated%20water%20goes%20to%20the%20lake%2C%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20there%20is%20always%20dilution%20from%20the%20rain%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20probably%20gets%2047%20or%2060%20days%20of%20rain%20across%20various%20months.%20So%2C%20based%20on%20this%20rain%2C%20there%20is%20always%20dilution%20in%20the%20lake.%20So%2C%20we%20do%20not%20purposefully%20do%20it%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20it%20to%20the%20lake%20is%20to%20dilute%20it%20with%20natural%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20explained%20earlier%2C%20treated%20wastewater%20that%20is%20further%20diluted%20with%20rainwater%20is%20diverted%20to%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%20Sihi%20Neerukere%20Lake.%20Here%2C%20it%20is%20further%20diluted%20with%20rainwater%2C%20and%20subsequently%20filtered%20through%20the%20earth%20to%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Sihi%20Neerukere%20Lake%20will%20dry%20up%20if%20no%20water%20flows%20into%20it.%20Devanahalli%20always%20had%20problems%20with%20drought.%20Back%20in%202015-16%2C%20this%20lake%20almost%20went%20dry.%20The%20local%20governing%20body%20asked%20the%20Government%20to%20send%20the%20treated%20wastewater%20to%20the%20lake%20because%20it%20would%20go%20defunct.%20That%20was%20the%20initial%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20treated%20wastewater%20is%20once%20again%20further%20diluted%20with%20rainwater%2C%20it%20is%20subsequently%20filtered%20through%20the%20earth%20to%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Phase%202%2C%20they%20used%20something%20called%20a%20shallow%20aquifer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20instead%20of%20digging%20a%20borewell%20at%201%2C000%20feet%2C%20you%20dig%20a%20filter%20borewell%20(shallow%20aquifer)%20at%20a%20maximum%20depth%20of%2050%20to%2090%20feet.%20Here%2C%20well%20water%20seeps%20again%20through%20natural%20filtration%20and%20enters%20the%20filter%20borewell.%20Filter%20borewells%20are%20essentially%20shallow%20borewells%20with%20pores%20in%20the%20pipe%20for%20filtering%2C%20and%20the%20plan%20was%20for%20about%20six%20or%20seven%20filter%20borewells%2C%20I%20believe%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20then%20undergoes%20another%20level%20of%20earth%20filtration%20before%20reaching%20another%20sump%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Ffit%3D1600%252C719%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fw%3D1600%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C135%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C225%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C345%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D1536%252C690%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C539%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG-20241030-WA0020-1730297386.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C67%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolutions%20to%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20crisis%20may%20lie%20in%20this%20model%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20they%20use%20shallow%20aquifer%20water%20from%20the%20filter%20borewells%2C%20directing%20it%20to%20the%20sump.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20added%20a%20more%20advanced%20treatment%20plant%2C%20where%20the%20disc%20filtration%20is%20now%20fully%20automated.%20This%20system%20includes%20a%20higher-grade%20activated%20carbon%20filter%2C%20multiple%20UV%20systems%20in%20parallel%2C%20and%20chlorine%20disinfection%2C%20after%20which%20the%20water%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20sump%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreviously%2C%20the%20sump%20received%20deep%20borewell%20water%20high%20in%20fluoride%2C%20contaminants%2C%20and%20dissolved%20salts.%20Now%2C%20these%20issues%20have%20decreased%20due%20to%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20water%2C%20and%20the%20psychological%20barrier%20is%20also%20gone%20since%20multiple%20levels%20of%20earth%20filtration%20are%20used%2C%20making%20the%20water%20safe%20to%20supply%20to%20the%20entire%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20is%20then%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20aquifer%20through%20a%20dug%20well%20and%20shallow%20filter%20borewells%2C%20treated%2C%20and%20then%20supplied%20to%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20quality%20meets%20IS%2010500%20standards.%20The%20TDS%20(total%20dissolved%20solids)%20averages%20below%20500%20ppm%2C%20compared%20to%201800%20ppm%20in%20deep%20borewells%2C%20and%20contains%20no%20fluoride%2C%20unlike%20deep%20borewell%20water.%20Making%20things%20better%2C%20Devanahalli%20residents%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20for%20the%20water%20since%20the%20local%20government%20body%20supplies%20it%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.